<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Wizards, this spell can actually be a necromancers best friend.  If the necromancer in your party gets very low on life, and you aren't ready to take on the next mob, cast an Eye of Zomm, let the necro throw a vampiric curse on it, and he gets healed for a minimal amount of mana on your part.  This may only work on PvP of course.  <BR>
