<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Morill</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-05-03 20:20:25</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>This spell is uber cool.  It should not be eliminated if only for this reason.  There are ways to use this spell, although there is tremendous need for intelligent researchers into the nature of magic to find a better version (ooc not possible by players of course).  1st; select if after you summon it and before your perception is moved to it and invis it.  This keeps it from being killed.  2nd; use it while right next to the zone or other safe spot (guard tower, etc).  3rd - use it to look in places like lava that are not safe (never tried but read a post that claimed this worked).  4th - left click the eye icon that shows this spell is active to cancel it as soon as there might be danger, and before it gets aggrod (not safe plan!) 5th - use it to look in places you and mobs cant get out of like pits and pools of water way down below you.</font></td></tr></table>
